author: Justin Hawkins Rides Again
description:
A few people have mentioned that Corey Feldman may have been referring to me when he recently described how he had been maligned by 'an English dude who sits there with a guitar and talks crap about people'.  I thought I would check his claims. All I can say is that I'm sorry Corey. 

To watch the full episode of The Magnificent Others With Billy Corgan, visit here: 
https://youtu.be/hTh0CCGJYIc?si=tyD0HedSHHL6K6Qr or listen to it here: 
https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast...
